This report shows the quality for map features that are usually

metadata.name: GHSPOP_COMPARISON
metadata.description:
The number of features per population count.
        This can give an estimate if mapping has been completed.

result.text: 17864 of People live in this Area following the GHS POP Dataset, with a total number of 101 buildings mapped in OSM. This results in 0.01 buildings per person, which together with a population density of 9429.34 people per sqkm,corresponds to a RED label in regards to Dataquality
